room_title: Escape room "The Tunnels Beneath" by The Great Escape of La Crosse in La Crosse
room_description: According to local lore there are long forgotten century old tunnels hidden beneath the city. Stories are passed from one generation to the next about how to find them and what they may contain… gangsters loot, hidden treasure, or maybe nothing at all? With a little luck, you’ve stumbled across an entrance and you’re about to find out… if you escape before your air runs out!
